        <body>
           <head><name xml:lang="eng">Cairo</name></head>
            <div type="positioning">
                <p><geo>30.05, 31.23</geo></p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <table>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft"><hi rend="bold">Interrogatives</hi></cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">who?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Most commonly dialects show reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">man</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Who is this man? – He is my friend</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red"><w ana="#vf_lex_who">mīn</w></hi> 
                            <w ana="#vf_mor_art_ass">iṛ</w>-<w ana="#vf_lex_man">ṛāgil</w> 
                            da? – da ṣaḥbi. (huwwa ṣaḥbi)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">whose?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Whose car is this? – This is our car. It’s small but it’s
                            good.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">di ʕaṛabiyyit <hi rend="red">mīn</hi>? – di l-ʕaṛabiyya
                            btaʕitna. (hiyya) ṣġayyara bassᴵ kwayyisa.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">what?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, what are you doing now? – I’m watching TV.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">bitiʕmili <hi rend="red">ʔēh</hi> dilwaʔti, yā faṭma? –
                            batfaṛṛag ʕa-t-tilifizyōn.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">why?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">A very common pattern are reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">li
                                + ’ayy</hi> or <hi rend="italic">li + ’ayy + šay’</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Why didn’t he come? – I don’t know. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ma-gā-š <hi rend="red">lēh</hi>? – ma-baʕṛaf-š.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">A very common pattern are reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">fī
                                + ’ayna</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where is my mobile (phone)? – Here it is!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">fēn</hi> il-mubayl bitāʕi? – ʔahó!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where to?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.) going? – I am going home.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">rāyiḥ/rayḥa <hi rend="red">(ʕala) fēn</hi>?
                            –ʕa-l-bēt.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where from?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.; sg./pl.) from? – I am/ We are from
                            Cairo.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ʔinta/ʔinti/ʔintu <hi rend="red">mnēn</hi>? – ʔana/ʔiḥna
                            min maṣr.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">when?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, when did you see Muhammad? – I saw him yesterday. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ya-faṭma, <hi rend="red">ʔimta</hi> šufti mḥammad? – šuftu
                            mbāriḥ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How are you (m./f.)? – I’m fine.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʔizzayy</hi>ak? – kwayyis, (il-ḥamdu li-llāh). / <hi rend="red">ʔizzayy</hi>ik? – kuwayyisa, (l-ḥamdu li-llāh).</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how much?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How much is half a kilo of lemons? – It’s 10 Pounds. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">nuṣṣᴵ kīlu lamūn <hi rend="red">b-kām</hi>? – bi-ʕašra
                            ginēh.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how many?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How many children do you (f.) have? – I have two daughters
                            and three sons.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ʕandak <hi rend="red">kām</hi> walad? – ʕandi bintēn
                            w-talat wilād.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">which?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">In which neighbourhood do you live? – We live in Zamalik. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">saknīn fi manṭiʔit <hi rend="red">ēh</hi>? – iḥna saknīn fi
                            z-zamālik.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Demonstratives</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">this</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Who is this man? – He is my friend</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">mīn iṛ-ṛāgil <hi rend="red">da</hi>? – da ṣaḥbi. (huwwa
                            ṣaḥbi)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                    </row>
